{"tid":2052913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"納指破碩 = 失業10+% + 疫情持續 + 美國暴亂","createTime":"2020-06-06T00:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T02:09:09.000Z","uid":342052,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5d817271d90103939b5ea0be0f2ede39385173","tid":2052913,"uid":342052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"所有壞消息當好消息炒,因為&quot;經濟&quot;沒有變得&quot;更壞&quot;!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0r6CKSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0r6CKSO.jpg&h=4d46840c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當下月失業數據持平或稍微回落,三大指數極有可能係TRUMP TRUMP連任前破頂...<br />\n睇返香港,國安法出台後中美口技戰白熱化,但無阻港股港匯走強,氣勢如紅,係高成交配合下好大機會一舉突破近兩月阻力位二萬五,展開升浪...上星期五既你有冇諗過?原因現實生活面臨種種困境包括減薪,涷薪,租金高企,長期戴口罩工作,買防疫物資,外出不方便,娛樂減少,但&quot;資產&quot;就繼續會爆升,因為情況沒有變得更壞! 下星期開市買咩好? 係咪應該買地產股? 連誠哥都買,股價又相對落後"},{"pid":"d9df7d1f34b0cb536e698f505c4aaf0c61ac92e7","tid":2052913,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T00:43:42.000Z","msg":"最壞情況已過，升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a3ed44d6fbc07d4d728c532de7d134c3c4f8cd","tid":2052913,"uid":77626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T00:45:23.000Z","msg":"支持樓豬開淡倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59494eb33a6e83be9f377151d9500e6659cdd4e","tid":2052913,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T00:47:15.000Z","msg":"失業率已經跌至13.3%<br />\n<br />\n暴動好小事，美國人慣曬<br />\n<br />\n疫情由每日3萬緩和到每日2萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf5e3112dd45205594